cs.LO, cs.LOgic, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.FL. 

The paper deals with model checking of open pushdown systems (OPD) w.r.t. standard branching temporal logics, which is a topic related to logic and formal methods. Therefore, cs.LOgic and cs.LO are likely categories. The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem, which suggests that it could belong to cs.PL (complexity theory) or cs.SE (software engineering). Finally, the paper deals with pushdown systems, which are a type of automata, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.FL (formal languages and automata theory).
